data.description: SELLER OFFERING $6000 TOWARDS CLOSING!!! Live the DREAM in the sought-after Waterscape subdivision! This beautiful craftsman style home built by Historymaker Homes has it ALL! 4 bedrooms, 3 baths + a study and game room. Open floor plan perfect for family living at its best. The large master suite, 2nd bedroom and full bath are on the first floor. 3rd and 4th bedrooms are upstairs along with a full bath and extra living area.  The main living area boasts a cozy fireplace and is open to an eat-in kitchen that features granite countertops, SS appliances, gas range, walk-in pantry and large island. Outdoors you will find an oversized covered patio with additional concrete, and landscaped with pea gravel. Neighborhood amenities include ponds, 2 pools, dog park, playgrounds, jogging paths and more.
